OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784772170
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FThe UK has withdrawn remaining
OL,7,Fdiplomatic staff from Iran as the
OL,8,Fconflict with the US continued to
OL,9,Fescalate with a 12th night of
OL,10,Fairstrikes.
OL,12,FA statement on the Foreign Office
OL,13,F(FCDO) website said: "Due to the
OL,14,Fsecurity situation, UK staff have been
OL,15,Ftemporarily withdrawn from Iran.
OL,17,F"Our embassy continues to operate
OL,18,Fremotely."
OL,26,@uD@VOUyD@AOUzD@JO]
