PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784772170
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FThe FCDO advises against all travel to
OL,7,FIran, saying British and dual British-
OL,8,FIranian residents face "significant
OL,9,Frisk of arrest, questioning or
OL,10,Fdetention".
OL,12,FA similar move was made in February
OL,13,Fahead of the start of US and Israel
OL,14,Fcombat operations.
OL,16,FUS Central Command said late on
OL,17,FWednesday that a 12th night of attacks
OL,18,Fwere designed to "further degrade
OL,19,FIran's ability to threaten civilian
OL,20,Fmariners and commercial vessels
OL,21,Ftransiting regional waters".
