OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784772170
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump had warned
OL,7,Fearlier that one bridge or power plant
OL,8,Fwould be destroyed for each ship shot
OL,9,Fat by Iran in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,F"From this point forward, any time the
OL,12,FIslamic Republic of Iran shoots at a
OL,13,Fship in the Strait of Hormuz, whether
OL,14,Fit be by Missile, Rocket, Drone, or
OL,15,Fany other device or weapon, the United
OL,16,FStates will bomb and destroy ONE
OL,17,FBRIDGE OR POWER PLANT," Mr Trump wrote
OL,18,Fon social media.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@WO]
