OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784772170
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FForeign minister Seyed Abbas Araghchi
OL,7,Falso said an "eye for an eye" approach
OL,8,Fwould be adopted by Iran.
OL,10,F"Any aggression against Iran,
OL,11,Fincluding our infrastructure, will
OL,12,Fcompel a powerful and decisive
OL,13,Fresponse," he posted on X on Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe 11th night of strikes on Iran into
OL,16,FWednesday saw air defences opening
OL,17,Ffire over the capital Tehran.
OL,19,FIran launched a missile attack on a
OL,20,FJordanian city while alerts were
OL,21,Fsounded in Bahrain and Saudi Arabia.
