OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FIran has responded to US attacks by
OL,7,Ftargeting energy infrastructure and
OL,8,Fdesalination plants which provide
OL,9,Fdrinking water in neighbouring Gulf
OL,10,Fcountries.
OL,12,FInternational law generally prohibits
OL,13,Fsuch attacks unless the infrastructure
OL,14,Fis being used for military purposes.
